==English==
=== Etymology ===
From Greek: ''a scattering''
===Noun===
'''Diaspora'''
# A [[dispersion]] of a group of people, mainly the [[:w:Jews]], from their native land.
# The Jews that were scattered among the [[:w:Gentiles]] after Babylonian captivity
